C1 -> C1 * (Q' G Q)(Q' G Q) = (t' G t)(t' G t) + (b' G b)(b' G b) + 2 * (t' G t)(b' G b)

C2 -> C2 * (Q' GTa Q)(Q' GTa Q) = (t' GTa t)(t' GTa t) + (b' GTa b)(b' GTa b) + 2 * (t' GTa t)(b' GTa b)

(t' GTa t)(t' GTa t) = 1/2 * [ (t' G t)(t' G t) - 1/3 * (t' G t)(t' G t) ] = 1/3 [ (t' G t)(t' G t) ]

---------------------
(t' G t)(t' G t)  :
---------------------

C1 * (t' G t)(t' G t) + 1/3 * C2 * (t' G t)(t' G t)  -> (C1 + 1/3 * C2) * (t' G t)(t' G t)